0039|- [HelpText]
0040|#PALETTE=<name of a .PAL file>
S   |         <                   >
0041|*(specification in GPLOT operation)
0042|*determines the color palette for the current graph.
0043|SDefault directory for .PAL files is the current data path
S   |                                         88888888888888888
0044|*and secondarily <Survo>\U\SYS .
S   |                 <     >
0045|*Each .PAL file is a text file with several lines of the form
0046|*  <color_index> <Red_intensity> <Green_intensity> <Blue_intensity>
S   |   <           > <             > <               > <              >
0047|*where <color_index> is 0,1,... (max 15 for EGA, for example) and
S   |       <           >
0048|*intensities are integers from 0 to 1000.
0049|*The PAL1.PAL file corresponds to the default colors obtained without
0050|*any PALETTE specification.
